window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Change is life. Consistency is a lie. Control is an illusion.</b></p> <p>Those are the words which greeted Tim upon his arrival in this new world which has become his home.</p> <p>They are the mantra that he has been forced to live.</p> <p>But are they true? Is there room for him to nudge his reality in the direction he wants to go?</p> <p>If he has to change so be it. Heâ€™ll ride the waves and make it work for him.</p> <p>This time he is determined to become Unstoppable.</p> <p><b>Book 3 in the next LitRPG saga from the Amazon bestselling author of </b><b><i>Life in Exile</i></b><b>, Sean Oswald, is perfect for fans of Dakota Krout, Luke Chmilenko, and Troy Osgood.</b></p>"; 
